                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">Fineness, not less
                            than</center>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">足白金 or 足鉑金
                            (Chuk Pak Kam)</center>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <center xmlns="http://www.xml.gov.hk/schemas/hklm/1.0">990</center>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
